ight, ending the effect on itself on a success.\", \"special\": null},{\"name\": \"Invisibility\", \"bonus\": null, \"damage\": \"The quasit magically turns invisible until it attacks or uses Scare, or until its concentration ends (as if concentrating on a spell) . Any equipment the quasit wears or carries is invisible with it.\", \"special\": null}]','Quasit.png'
