('Air elemental','124','5',NULL,'0ft., fly 90ft. (hover)','15',NULL,'12d10+24',5,2,5,2,-2,0,-2,2,5,2,-2,0,-2,'darkvision 60 ft.','<strong>Damage Resistance</strong> lightning, thunder, 🔨, 🏹, and ⚔️ from nonmagical weapons<br><br><strong>Status Immunities</strong> exhaustion, grappled, paralyzed, petrified, poisoned, prone, restrained, unconscious<br><br><strong>Air Form</strong> The elemental can enter a hostile creature\'s space and stop there. It can move through a space as narrow as 1 inch wide without squeezing.','Large Elemental','arctic,cave,coast,desert,dungeon,forest,grassland,mountain,ruins,swamp,underground,planar','[]',NULL,'[]','[{\"name\": \"Slam\", \"bonus\": \"8\", \"damage\": \"2d8+5 🔨\", \"special\": null},{\"name\": \"Whirlwind\", \"bonus\": null, \"damage\": \"Recharge: 1d3+3 rounds\", \"special\": \"Each creature in the elemental\'s space must make a DC 13 Strength saving throw. On a failure, a target takes 3d8+2 🔨 damage and is flung up 20 feet away from the elemental in a random direction and knocked prone. If a thrown target strikes an object, such as a wall or floor, the target takes 1d6 🔨 damage for every 10 feet it was thrown. If the target is thrown at another creature, that creature must succeed on a DC 13 Dexterity saving throw or take the same damage and be knocked prone.If the saving throw is successful, the target takes half the 🔨 damage and isn\'t flung away or knocked prone.\"}]','Air elemental.png'
,1,955,'[{\"name\": \"Double Slam\", \"actions\": [\"Slam\",\"Slam\"], \"type\": \"multiattack\"}]')");


