('Giant vulture','329','1',NULL,'10ft., fly 60ft.','10',NULL,'3d10+6',0,2,0,2,-2,1,-2,2,0,2,-2,1,-2,'passive Perception 13, Keen Sight and Smell','<strong>Pack Tactics.</strong> The vulture has advantage on an attack roll against a creature if at least one of the vulture\'s allies is within 5 feet of the creature and the ally isn\'t incapacitated.','Large Beast','desert,grassland,ruins','[{ \"name\": \"Perception\", \"bonus\": \"3\"}]',NULL,'[]','[{\"name\": \"Beak\", \"bonus\": \"4\", \"damage\": \"1d4+2 ⚔️\", \"special\": null},{\"name\": \"Talons\", \"bonus\": \"4\", \"damage\": \"2d6+2 ⚔️\", \"special\": null}]','Giant vulture.png'
